<div>Hmm. &quot;_enum&quot; has possibilities.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>How about using a * in the name, to represent where the match is? &nbsp;E.G., &nbsp;btl_usnic_*_enum?</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>It's a string, so it's not just limited to letters and underscores.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
